Hoddesdon, Hertfordshire 2003.  32 year old Dave King had just left the gym when the white transit van slowed down and the passenger carefully took aim and let fire a torrent of bullets from the AK47.&#13;
&#13;
In this episode of the UK True Crime weekly podcast I look at events leading up to this shooting and what happened next.&#13;
